OL,7,FThe father and daughter were at the
OL,8,FAriana Grande concert in May 2017 and
OL,9,Fsuffered life-changing injuries, with
OL,10,FMr Hibbert left with a spinal cord
OL,11,Finjury and Miss Hibbert facing severe
OL,12,Fbrain damage.
OL,14,FHowever, Mr Hall has claimed that the
OL,15,Fattack, in which Salman Abedi
OL,16,Fdetonated a homemade rucksack bomb in
OL,17,Fthe crowd of concert-goers, was faked.
