OL,7,FThe author has been accused of
OL,8,Fvisiting the homes and workplaces of
OL,9,Fthose injured in the attack `
OL,10,Fincluding Miss Hibbert's home ` and
OL,11,Frecording footage of them.
OL,13,FIn a ruling last month, in a bid for
OL,14,Fsummary judgement ` a legal step to
OL,15,Fdecide parts of the case without a
OL,16,Ftrial ` on several parts of the case's
OL,17,Fbackground.
