OL,7,FHe said it was "fanciful" to suggest
OL,8,Fthat Abedi did not die and "still more
OL,9,Ffanciful" to argue the bomber was an
OL,10,Fintelligence asset.
OL,12,FAt a remote hearing on Wednesday, 13
OL,13,FMarch, Mr Hall asked for the go-ahead
OL,14,Fto challenge the judge at the High
OL,15,FCourt's decision.
OL,17,FRepresenting himself, he said: "There
OL,18,Fseems to be a lack of knowledge within
OL,19,Fthe judiciary about false flag
OL,20,Fterrorism."
