OL,7,FMr Hall claimed that "Nato countries"
OL,8,Fhad carried out hoax events "to fool
OL,9,Fthe public into thinking they are
OL,10,Funder attack", adding: "It is very
OL,11,Fconcerning that the judiciary does not
OL,12,Fseem to be aware of it."
OL,14,FHe subsequently claimed the inquiry
OL,15,Finto the Manchester Arena attack was
OL,16,F"corrupt" and that the legal claim
OL,17,Fagainst him "is being used for an
OL,18,Fulterior political purpose".
