OL,7,F"It is the real bomb attack hypothesis
OL,8,Fthat is implausible because the
OL,9,Fevidence does not point to it," Mr
OL,10,FHall continued in the hearing attended
OL,11,Fby more than 120 people.
OL,13,FJudge Davison denied Mr Hall
OL,14,Fpermission to bring an appeal against
OL,15,Fhis previous judgment.
OL,17,FHe said: "Nothing that you have said
OL,18,Famounts to, in my view, an argument
OL,19,Fthat would have a real prospect of
OL,20,Fsuccess in an appeal."
